N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 630.9 - Nondiscrimination

State Regulations

No person shall on the ground of sex, age, race, color, religion, or national origin be excluded from participating in, be denied the
benefits of, or be subjected to discrimination under, any program or activity
governed by article 23-B of the Labor Law and this Part. Notes
